OL,4,Cdeath of talented cyclist
OL,6,FA man whose dangerous driving caused
OL,7,Fthe death of a Welsh triathlon and
OL,8,FIronman star has been jailed.
OL,10,FVasile Barbu, 49, was found guilty by
OL,11,FCardiff Crown Court for causing death
OL,12,Fby dangerous driving of Rebecca Comins.
OL,14,FThe collision happened on Thursday 2
OL,15,FJune 2022 when Barbu was driving a as
OL,16,Fdriving a white Vauxhall Movano van on
OL,17,Fthe A40 near Raglan, Monmouthshire.
OL,19,FParamedics from the Welsh Ambulance
OL,20,FService attended and confirmed that
OL,21,FRebecca had died at the scene.
