OL,4,Cdeath of talented cyclist
OL,6,FBarbu has been sentenced to four years
OL,7,Fin prison and disqualified from
OL,8,Fdriving for four years.
OL,10,FSenior investigating officer, PS Shane
OL,11,FDraper from Gwent Police said:
OL,12,F"Rebecca was an experienced and
OL,13,Ftalented cyclist ` she did everything
OL,14,Fshe could to stay safe of the roads `
OL,15,Fbut the actions of a fellow road user
OL,16,Fsaw her life tragically cut short.
OL,18,F"Driving is a privilege, and not
OL,19,Fsomething that should be taken for
OL,20,Fgranted or taken lightly.
