OL,4,Cdeath of talented cyclist
OL,6,F"This is reminder to everyone who gets
OL,7,Fbehind the wheel ` you are in control
OL,8,Fof a potentially dangerous machine -
OL,9,Fyour responsibility isn't just to
OL,10,Fensure your own safety, but the safety
OL,11,Fof everyone around you.
OL,13,F"I would like to thank and commend the
OL,14,Ffamily for their strength during this
OL,15,Fdifficult time and I hope that this
OL,16,Fconviction helps provide them with
OL,17,Fsome closure as they continue to
OL,18,Fprocess their loss. My thoughts remain
OL,19,Fwith them".
